Module com.javarepowizards.portfoliomanager
Package com.javarepowizards.portfoliomanager.models

Class StockData

java.lang.Object
com.javarepowizards.portfoliomanager.models.StockData
public class StockData extends Object
The StockData class models the financial data for a single stock on a particular date. It contains key information such as price, volume, and other trading metrics.
